    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1173659029">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1173659029" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1173659029" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1173659029">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55421067/">holly2007</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">Machiavelli首次将政治与伦理分开，拔擢政治到技艺之层面，政治学由此诞生。作者编选的黑语录，尖刻深入，读之衷心凛凛，可谓欧版《韩非子》；尤其第三部《人间篇》，值得反复揣摩。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1122631895">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1122631895" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1122631895" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1122631895">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunshineonlyme/">清溪</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">他的君主论深奥难读，盐野七生用摘录文章让入门的读者了解君主论作者所表达的意图。领导要有战略性眼光与人格魅力。这本书切合实际，政治如职场，适合管理人士去看。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
